http://hostname:port/kettle/runTrans/?trans=/path/to/transname&level=DebugLevel&ParameterName=ParameterValue*
http://hostname:port/kettle/runJob/?job=/path/to/jobname&level=DebugLevel&ParameterName=ParameterValue*


http://127.0.0.1:8080/kettle/runJob/?job=/time
http://127.0.0.1:8080/kettle/runTrans/?trans=/time_trans


For file (XML) based transformations:http://*username:password@hostname:port/kettle/executeTrans/?trans=PathTo{}File*
For transformations stored in a repository:http://*username:password@hostname:port/kettle/executeTrans/?rep=RepositoryName&user=RepositoryUser&pass=RepositoryPassword&trans=PathTo{}TransformationInRepository*
Please note that you need to replace forward slashes with %2F in your browser.  That leads to this URL in our example:


http://127.0.0.1:8080/kettle/status/

http://127.0.0.1:8080/kettle/status/?xml=true

http://host:port/kettle/status <-- status page
http://host:port/kettle/status?xml=true <-- machine readable status page



