http://wiki.pentaho.com/display/EAI/JDBC+and+SQL+Reference


jdbc:pdi://localhost:8084/kettle?debugtrans=/tmp/jdbc.ktr

http://127.0.0.1:8080/kettle?debugtrans==/time_trans